Where your RTFIE sits

RTFIE is not just CV.

It spans multiple layers:
	•	Perception (CV) → see the scene
	•	Representation (FEP) → encode field
	•	Inference → pattern matching
	•	Reasoning → hypothesis generation
	•	Narrative → output structured explanation
	•	Governance → avoid identity claims

That’s why it feels powerful—it’s a multi-layer system, not a single model.

